# main-no-module

[![NPM version][npm-image]][npm-url]

> A module with main and api but no usage

## Installation

Install `main-no-module` using [npm](https://www.npmjs.com/):

```bash
npm install --save main-no-module
```

| b | `Mixed` | ... |
